title: Prince invites fans to party with him at Paisley Park
text: Prince invites fans to party with him at Paisley Park By Associated Press | October 26, 2015 @ 12:25 pm FILE - In this Feb. 4, 2007 file photo, Prince performs during the halftime show at Super Bowl XLI in Miami. In recent weeks Prince has hosted late-night jam sessions where he has serenaded Madonna and celebrated the Minnesota Lynx's WNBA championship. Hundreds of fans descended on suburban Paisley Park Studios on Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015 paying $10 each to hear Prince and his band raise the roof until 3 a.m. (AP Photo/Amy Sancetta, File)
